RECORDS: 1

==== ENTRY 1 ====
HEADWORD: Workless
<hw>Work"less</hw>, <pos>a.</pos> <sn>1.</sn> <def>Without work; not
laboring; <as>as, many people were still
<ex>workless</ex></as>.</def>⟦br⟧
[<source>1913 Webster</source>]</p>

<p><sn>2.</sn> <def>Not carried out in practice; not exemplified in
fact; <as>as, <ex>workless</ex> faith</as>.</def> <mark>[Obs.]</mark>
<rj><au>Sir T. More.</au></rj>⟦br⟧
[<source>1913 Webster</source>]</p>

<p><ent>Workman</ent>⟦br⟧
